/http://gb.cri.cn/27824/2012/07/06/2625s3758932.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>。7月30日返回大连造船新厂码头，历时25天，是历次海试中时间最长的一次<ref>{{cite web|url=http://mil.sohu.com/20120730/n349380309.shtml|title=中国航母平台第九次海试返回　时间创纪录达25天|publisher=国际在线|date=2012-07-30|language=zh-hans|access-date=2012-07-30|archive-date=2013-10-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131021131621/http://mil.sohu.com/20120730/n349380309.shtml|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref name="shanghaidaily">{{cite news|url=http://www.shanghaidaily.com/national/J15-jets-on-deck-as-carrier-sets-off-on-longest-sea-trials/shdaily.shtml|title=J-15 jets on deck as carrier sets off on longest sea trials|date=2012-07-12|newspaper=Shanghai Daily|accessdate=2014-01-04|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20141110082316/http://www.shanghaidaily.com/national/J15-jets-on-deck-as-carrier-sets-off-on-longest-sea-trials/shdaily.shtml|archivedate=2014-11-10|author=Yang, Jian|dead-url=no}}</ref>。8月27日，中国大陸航空母舰平台开始第10次海试。此次试航期间，2012年第15号台风“布拉万”8月28日抵达黄海海域，此次海试是测试在恶劣海况下的航行能力<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.chinanews.com/mil/2012/08-27/4137182.shtml|title=中国航母平台第十次海试出航将迎台风洗礼|publisher=中国新闻网|date=2012-08-27|language=zh-hans|access-date=2012-08-28|archive-date=2021-03-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210310015449/http://www.chinanews.com/mil/2012/08-27/4137182.shtml|dead-url=no}}</ref>。历时4天，时长不足70小时，8月30日停靠大连港码头<ref>{{cite web|url=http://mil.news.sina.com.cn/2012-08-31/1006699606.html|title=中国航母第十次海试结束创下时长最短纪录|publisher=中新社|date=2012-08-31|language=zh-hans|author=|access-date=2012-09-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131021130834/http://mil.news.sina.com.cn/2012-08-31/1006699606.html|archive-date=2013-10-21|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。

